          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='13'>Evidence from Analysis</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='12'>• UPI and credit card transaction volumes exhibit a strong positive relationship.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='12'>• Correlation between UPI volume and credit card volume = 0.983.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='12'>• SBI Card customer growth and spending are strongly correlated (0.975).</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='12'>• Regression model explains 95.1% of spending variation.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='12'>• FY26 customer base forecast = 2.28 crore cards.</run>
          </formatted-text>
