        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='34516' id='15' type-v2='text' w='36320' x='963' y='59618'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='12'>Key Insight</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='12'>UPI transaction volume increased from 9,152 million transactions in FY18 to 1.86 million million transactions in FY25. Despite rapid UPI adoption, credit card transaction volume also grew from 14,052 million to 47,741 million transactions. The strong positive correlation (0.983) suggests that digital payment methods expanded together rather than replacing one another.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
