          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#75a1c7' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='12'>SBI Card&apos;s customer base grew from 0.63 crore cards in FY18 to 2.08 crore cards in FY25. Spending increased from ₹79.8K crore to ₹333.5K crore over the same period. The correlation between customer base and spending is 0.975, indicating that customer acquisition strongly drives transaction value growth.</run>
